# ComputeIK.srv
# =============
# Request: desired end-effector position in the XY plane
float64 target_x
float64 target_y
---
# Response
bool    success          # True  → IK solution found
string  message          # Human-readable status / error description
float64 theta1           # Joint 1 angle  [rad]
float64 theta2           # Joint 2 angle  [rad]
float64 theta3           # Joint 3 angle  [rad] (always 0.0 in this impl.)